  <brief_title>Observational Study of the Conjugated Rehabilitation on Children With Cerebral Palsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Observational Study of the Conventional Rehabilitation and Traditional Korean Medicine Conjugated Rehabilitation on Children With Cerebral Palsy</official_title>
