    <measure>Change from baseline on PEDI scores at week 26 and 52</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline, Week 26, Week 52</time_frame>
    <description>The PEDI measures abilities in the three functional domains of self-care, mobility and social function with 217 questions.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
